                     <interp inst="t18371127-76-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="shoplifting"></interp> for stealing, on the <rs id="t18371127-cd-55" type="crimeDate">
                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18371127-76-offence-1 t18371127-cd-55"></join>7th of November</rs>, 2 bottles, value 3<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.; and 1 pint of sauce, value, 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 9<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.; the gools of <persName id="t18371127-name-469" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18371127-name-469" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18371127-name-469" type="surname" value="BEALE"></interp>
